{
  "stem": "1704.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At one stop we put something, a sheet or something, on the train on top, with a Star of David on it, you know, so they would see it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we could hear shooting, that side and that side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, the Americans and the Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did not know that our train was destined to have an accident in the River Elbe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the plan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But seeing that the Americans and the Russians came close, the guards got a bit scared and were a bit friendly towards us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the accident did not happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one morning, knock knock at the door.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Open up, open up, we're free.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Russians are here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we all went to the village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was not so lucky to get-- we had to go into the homes of the Germans, and me and two other--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we did not know we were in the River Elbe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To another camp, that was all we knew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we didn't know this much, but there was one wagon with the leaders in it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I gave you a piece of paper that would say that it was in the train, that it was signed by a couple of people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, they were in the passenger's wagon, keeping-- because I had to go every day when somebody died, I had to go to that compartment and say, such and such died, such and such died, so that they could keep the lists, which was a good thing, of course.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the matron of the-- who was matron in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't notice anything with the guards.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe the ones in the-- you know, the leaders might have had contact with them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the train?",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
